'''Koonfurta Afrika''' ({{lang-en|Southern Africa}}; {{lang-ar|أفريقيا الجنوبية}}) waa gobolka ugu xiga dhinaca [[koonfur]]ta qaarada [[Afrika]], taasi oo aad ugu kala duwan deegaan ahaan, juquraafi ahaan iyo siyaasad ahaan dhamaan gobolada kale ee qaarada. Sida ku xusan qawaaniinta gobolada ee dejisay [[QM|Jimciyada Qarama Midoobay]]<ref>{{cite web | url = http://unstats.un.org/unsd/methods/m49/m49regin.htm| title = Composition of macro geographical (continental) regions, geographical sub-regions, and selected economic and other groupings | publisher = United Nations| date = 2013-10-31 | accessdate = 2015-01-28}}</ref> deegaanka Koonfurta Afrika waxay ka kooban tahay ilaa 11 wadan<ref>{{cite web|url=http://millenniumindicators.un.org/unsd/methods/m49/m49regin.htm|title=United Nations Statistics Division- Standard Country and Area Codes Classifications (M49)|work=un.org}}</ref> kuwaasi oo kala ah: [[Angola]], [[Botswana]], [[Lesotho]], [[Malawi]], [[Mozambique]], [[Namibia]], [[South Africa]], [[Swaziland]], [[Tanzania]], [[Zambia]], iyo [[Zimbabwe]].


